48 bool storeState(moveit_msgs::SaveRobotStateToWarehouse::Request& request,
49  moveit_msgs::SaveRobotStateToWarehouse::Response& response, moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage* rs)
50 {
51  if (request.name.empty())
52  {
53  ROS_ERROR("You must specify a name to store a state");
54  return (response.success = false);
55  }
56  rs->addRobotState(request.state, request.name, request.robot);
57  return (response.success = true);
58 }
59 
60 bool listStates(moveit_msgs::ListRobotStatesInWarehouse::Request& request,
61  moveit_msgs::ListRobotStatesInWarehouse::Response& response, moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage* rs)
62 {
63  if (request.regex.empty())
64  {
65  rs->getKnownRobotStates(response.states, request.robot);
66  }
67  else
68  {
69  rs->getKnownRobotStates(request.regex, response.states, request.robot);
70  }
71  return true;
72 }
73 
74 bool hasState(moveit_msgs::CheckIfRobotStateExistsInWarehouse::Request& request,
75  moveit_msgs::CheckIfRobotStateExistsInWarehouse::Response& response,
76  moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage* rs)
77 {
78  response.exists = rs->hasRobotState(request.name, request.robot);
79  return true;
80 }

82 bool getState(moveit_msgs::GetRobotStateFromWarehouse::Request& request,
83  moveit_msgs::GetRobotStateFromWarehouse::Response& response, moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage* rs)
84 {
85  if (!rs->hasRobotState(request.name, request.robot))
86  {
87  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("No state called '" << request.name << "' for robot '" << request.robot << "'.");
88  moveit_msgs::RobotState dummy;
89  response.state = dummy;
90  return false;
91  }
92  moveit_warehouse::RobotStateWithMetadata state_buffer;
93  rs->getRobotState(state_buffer, request.name, request.robot);
94  response.state = static_cast<const moveit_msgs::RobotState&>(*state_buffer);
95  return true;
96 }
97 
98 bool renameState(moveit_msgs::RenameRobotStateInWarehouse::Request& request,
99  moveit_msgs::RenameRobotStateInWarehouse::Response& /*response*/,
100  moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage* rs)
101 {
102  if (!rs->hasRobotState(request.old_name, request.robot))
103  {
104  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("No state called '" << request.old_name << "' for robot '" << request.robot << "'.");
105  return false;
106  }
107  rs->renameRobotState(request.old_name, request.new_name, request.robot);
108  return true;
109 }
110 
111 bool deleteState(moveit_msgs::DeleteRobotStateFromWarehouse::Request& request,
112  moveit_msgs::DeleteRobotStateFromWarehouse::Response& /*response*/,
113  moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage* rs)
114 {
115  if (!rs->hasRobotState(request.name, request.robot))
116  {
117  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("No state called '" << request.name << "' for robot '" << request.robot << "'.");
118  return false;
119  }
120  rs->removeRobotState(request.name, request.robot);
121  return true;
122 }

124 int main(int argc, char** argv)
125 {
126  ros::init(argc, argv, "moveit_warehouse_services");
127 
128  ros::AsyncSpinner spinner(1);
129  spinner.start();
130 
131  ros::NodeHandle node;
132  std::string host;
133 
134  int port;
135  float connection_timeout;
136  int connection_retries;
137 
138  node.param<std::string>("warehouse_host", host, "localhost");
139  node.param<int>("warehouse_port", port, 33829);
140  node.param<float>("warehouse_db_connection_timeout", connection_timeout, 5.0);
141  node.param<int>("warehouse_db_connection_retries", connection_retries, 5);
142 
143  warehouse_ros::DatabaseConnection::Ptr conn;
144 
145  try
146  {
147  conn = moveit_warehouse::loadDatabase();
148  conn->setParams(host, port, connection_timeout);
149 
150  ROS_INFO("Connecting to warehouse on %s:%d", host.c_str(), port);
151  int tries = 0;
152  while (!conn->connect())
153  {
154  ++tries;
155  ROS_WARN("Failed to connect to DB on %s:%d (try %d/%d).", host.c_str(), port, tries, connection_retries);
156  if (tries == connection_retries)
157  {
158  ROS_FATAL("Failed to connect too many times, giving up");
159  return 1;
160  }
161  }
162  }
163  catch (std::exception& ex)
164  {
165  ROS_ERROR("%s", ex.what());
166  return 1;
167  }
168 
169  moveit_warehouse::RobotStateStorage rs(conn);
170 
171  std::vector<std::string> names;
172  rs.getKnownRobotStates(names);
173  if (names.empty())
174  ROS_INFO("There are no previously stored robot states");
175  else
176  {
177  ROS_INFO("Previously stored robot states:");
178  for (const std::string& name : names)
179  ROS_INFO(" * %s", name.c_str());
180  }
181 
182  boost::function<bool(moveit_msgs::SaveRobotStateToWarehouse::Request & request,
183  moveit_msgs::SaveRobotStateToWarehouse::Response & response)>
184  save_cb = boost::bind(&storeState, _1, _2, &rs);
185 
186  boost::function<bool(moveit_msgs::ListRobotStatesInWarehouse::Request & request,
187  moveit_msgs::ListRobotStatesInWarehouse::Response & response)>
188  list_cb = boost::bind(&listStates, _1, _2, &rs);
189 
190  boost::function<bool(moveit_msgs::GetRobotStateFromWarehouse::Request & request,
191  moveit_msgs::GetRobotStateFromWarehouse::Response & response)>
192  get_cb = boost::bind(&getState, _1, _2, &rs);
193 
194  boost::function<bool(moveit_msgs::CheckIfRobotStateExistsInWarehouse::Request & request,
195  moveit_msgs::CheckIfRobotStateExistsInWarehouse::Response & response)>
196  has_cb = boost::bind(&hasState, _1, _2, &rs);
197 
198  boost::function<bool(moveit_msgs::RenameRobotStateInWarehouse::Request & request,
199  moveit_msgs::RenameRobotStateInWarehouse::Response & response)>
200  rename_cb = boost::bind(&renameState, _1, _2, &rs);
201 
202  boost::function<bool(moveit_msgs::DeleteRobotStateFromWarehouse::Request & request,
203  moveit_msgs::DeleteRobotStateFromWarehouse::Response & response)>
204  delete_cb = boost::bind(&deleteState, _1, _2, &rs);
205 
206  ros::ServiceServer save_state_server = node.advertiseService("save_robot_state", save_cb);
207  ros::ServiceServer list_states_server = node.advertiseService("list_robot_states", list_cb);
208  ros::ServiceServer get_state_server = node.advertiseService("get_robot_state", get_cb);
209  ros::ServiceServer has_state_server = node.advertiseService("has_robot_state", has_cb);
210  ros::ServiceServer rename_state_server = node.advertiseService("rename_robot_state", rename_cb);
211  ros::ServiceServer delete_state_server = node.advertiseService("delete_robot_state", delete_cb);
212 
213  ros::waitForShutdown();
214  return 0;
215 }
